public enum EScenarioSetPermutationLayer
extends java.lang.Enum<EScenarioSetPermutationLayer>

some Scenarios need to be permuted into ScenarioSets differently depending on what the ScenarioSet is used for. For example, you can only run 1 database scenario with a web application at a time, while you can run multiple database scenarios with PHP_CORE

Author:
Matt Ficken
